title: Simple processing for raw microarray and bulk RNA data
text: GEO data downloaded MetaIntegrator. includes expr slot contains expression data, normalized data authors Microarray: Supplemental data files downloaded GEOquery, raw .CEL files Affymetrix microarray platform RNAseq: gene count matrix generated NCBI’s standardized pipeline, well annotation file used pipeline, downloaded. Microarry: Affymetrix data uses Affy package workflow. Agilent data uses limma package workflow RNAseq: Uses DESeq2 workflow. Defaults vst normalization, can also use rlog original expr slot reassigned exprGEO slot, indicate represents authors’ normalized data raw, non-normalized data supplemental files assigned exprRAW slot user normalized data added expr slot, slot used downstream applications using MetaIntegrator GEO objects expression slots (.e. expr, exprRAW, exprGEO) visualized boxplots evaluate normalization process
